title: Electoral Map
subtitle: Map
view-if: year = 1928 and month >= 2
new-page: true
max-visits: 1
tags: event

@ca_map_scene
title: The Political Map of California

The state's districts, colored by the party currently holding each seat.

{!<div id="ca-map-container" style="margin: 12px 0;"></div>!}
{!<script>
  // Runs once the scene's HTML is inserted into the page.
  // Safe to call again if the player revisits this scene — the container is cleared each time.
  renderCADistrictMap("#ca-map-container", {
    width: 640,
    height: 720,
    onClick: function(d) {
      // Example hook: stash the clicked district number into a Dendry quality
      // so later scenes/choices can reference it.
      dendryUI.dendryEngine.state.qualities["selected_district"] = d.properties.DISTRICT;
    }
  });
</script>!}

- @next_scene: Continue
